the honor was bestowed
in recognition of Tower's

01:02:26.251 --> 01:02:28.913
high profile image, marketing
and merchandising strength,

01:02:29.212 --> 01:02:31.123
and fiscal responsibility.

01:02:33.341 --> 01:02:35.423
so starting in 1984,
you had michael jackson,

01:02:35.718 --> 01:02:37.379
and madonna, and bruce
springsteen, and prince,

01:02:37.679 --> 01:02:39.135
and then you had
the hair metal bands

01:02:39.430 --> 01:02:41.091
and then you had
the grunge era,

01:02:41.391 --> 01:02:43.097
and then you had
hootie and the blowfish,

01:02:43.393 --> 01:02:45.008
and then you had
this entire period

01:02:45.311 --> 01:02:47.176
'84 to 2000,
it's no coincidence

01:02:47.480 --> 01:02:49.391
that hip hop had
its booming growth

01:02:49.691 --> 01:02:50.931
during this period.

01:02:51.234 --> 01:02:52.940
then you had boy bands
and britney spears

01:02:53.236 --> 01:02:55.443
and christina aguilera,
and all th ese acts

01:02:55.738 --> 01:02:58.104
that took advantage of teen
pop stuff that was big.

01:02:58.408 --> 01:03:00.148
so it was just
one bomb exploding

01:03:00.451 --> 01:03:02.407
after another in music.

01:03:02.704 --> 01:03:03.864
Tower was the center of it all.

