01:30:31.809 --> 01:30:33.470
for Tower, for each other.

01:30:33.770 --> 01:30:34.885
people went to music stores,

01:30:35.188 --> 01:30:37.099
they listened to music,
it was an experience

01:30:37.398 --> 01:30:38.979
going in to a store
